&lt;p>This sketch was of a aggressive ninja ready for an attack!&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/2010_a_tree.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/2010_a_tree.jpg" alt="2010_a_tree" title="2010_a_tree">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
